{"tid":693365,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又係鄰國] Android手機連不明WiFi遭入侵","createTime":"2018-06-07T11:56:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-07T11:56:41.000Z","uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f1ed3c703258a738e04410fc744502d586dc20a6","tid":693365,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T11:56:25.000Z","msg":"一隻名為「少爺殭屍網路」的病毒正在擴散，目前全球已有6000宗Android手機被入侵的個案。<br />\n<br />\n台灣傳媒報道，行政院國家資通安全會報技術服務中心發現，只要使用無線路由器(Router)連上手機，或者使用手機連上不明的WiFi，就可能被黑客入侵。<br />\n<br />\n中心指出，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>攻勢來自中國與北韓邊界</strong></span>，利用各國網路平台服務商主機，針對亞洲區域家用路由器進行劫持攻擊，誘騙民眾連線並安裝惡意程式。<br />\n<br />\n目前，全球已有6000宗個案，被盜的個人資料超過100萬個。台灣已有近100人的手機被入侵。"},{"pid":"f36c3a4011f885a107d1dc92b2dcdc75d19431fb","tid":693365,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T11:56:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/1861552\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F1861552&d=49PVwSL8tEzP4Prf3PHnqRxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=0d485094\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/1861552</a>"}]}